But it works (seems to...)

## Usage

1. Install Rust and clone this repository.
2. Build the project with `cargo build`.
3. Run the tool using `cargo run`.

### Authorized Options

TemplateTool supports the following command-line options:

- `-i input_filename`: Specify the input job file. This file contains a list of tasks to perform.
- `-l log_level`: Set the log level for the app.

### Input Job File Description

This file can contain multiple sections describing the jobs to do.
A job is described by a section of multiple lines:
- An input filename (which contains tokens to replace)
- An output filename (for the result)
- Multiple lines for the replacements to do
- An end of job description

The syntax of a line is:
keyword [`if`, `of`, `r`, `do`] separator [`;`] optional_token separator [`;`] optional_value

Example:
if;filename    
of;filename     
r;token;string  
do;             

### Token Replacement

TemplateTool allows you to specify multiple tokens and their corresponding values for replacement in the destination files. Tokens are placeholders within your template files (e.g., `{{PROJECT_NAME}}`, `{{AUTHOR}}`). When generating a new project, you can provide values for these tokens, and TemplateTool will automatically replace them throughout the generated files. This enables flexible and dynamic project customization based on your input.

#### Example: Personal Card Generation for Home Assistant

The generic card is provided in the file `TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml`, which contains `$$$TITRE$$$` to be replaced by the title of the card and `$$$TST$$$` to be replaced by the name of the virtual thermostat.
The example generates multiple cards using the job file description like this:

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_alexis-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Chambre Alexis  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_alexis  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_bureau-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Bureau  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_bureau  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_ch_bas-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Chambre bas  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_ch_bas  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_cuisam-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Cuisine  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_cuisam  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_elisa-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Chambre Elisa  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_elisa  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_garage-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;Garage  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_garage  
do;  

if;TEMPLATE-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
of;vt_sdb_bas-carte-thermostat-perso.yaml  
r;$$$TITRE$$$;SDB bas  
r;$$$TST$$$;vt_sdb_bas  
r;#33ccff;#000000  
do;

